===============================

version number: 1.0
author: JACKY KIMANI
Overview
--------

Collect thoughts and events

Installation / Usage
--------------------

To install use pip:

    $ pip install Thought Book


Or clone the repo:

    $ git clone https://github.com/ndukulu2/Thought Book.git
    $ python setup.py install
